title: 6 KCRW albums
description:
6 KCRW Albums, ripped with EAC and encoded with LAME set at 192Kbit/sec
All MP3s have embedded album covers

If you guys like what you hear, I strongly urge you to buy the compilations or donate to the station (KCRW.com).
